```
!Help                   Lists available commands
!UserInfo               Displays the user's information
!Slap [@user]           Slaps the mentioned user
!FlipCoin               Returns "Heads" or "Tails"
!GenNumber [min] [max]  Returns a random number
!Giveaways              DM's a link for giveaways
!Owner                  Displays the servers owner
!Poke [@user]           Pokes a user
!Kill [@user]           Attempts to kill a user
!level [@user]          Displays your activity level
!Invite                 Get the link to invite me to your server
!Prices                 Get the link for prices
!Randommember           Gets a random member for you
```
